## Privacy / provenance note

This is an **always-private** repo used as the durable archive. It deliberately
**commits** scarce artifacts and evidence — they're too hard to re-source to risk
losing. Consequently it may contain proprietary material and identifying details.
**Keep it private; do not push to a shared or public remote.** Only reproducible
blobs (large images/dumps) are git-ignored. The project's own
[LICENSE](LICENSE) covers the written record and any scripts authored here — not
third-party artifacts, which keep their own terms (see [docs/PRIVACY.md](docs/PRIVACY.md)).
